## Console Logging Rules

### Console Output Language

- All `console.log()`, `console.error()`, `console.warn()`, `console.info()` messages MUST be written in Korean
- Use Korean for debugging messages, error messages, and informational messages
- Write log messages clearly and understandably

### Console Logging Best Practices

- Use console logs only in development environment (remove in production)
- Use meaningful emojis or icons to distinguish logs
- Use appropriate console methods based on log level
- Do not include sensitive information in logs

